OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776449466
OL,3,CRail services set to resume after day
OL,4,Cof travel chaos
OL,6,FRail services are expected to resume
OL,7,Fafter damage to overhead wire saw all
OL,8,Ftrains cancelled or delayed to and
OL,9,Ffrom a major UK railway station.
OL,11,FAll trains running through Manchester
OL,12,FPiccadilly faced long delays or were
OL,13,Fcancelled entirely on Thursday, 17
OL,14,FApril, with operators telling
OL,15,Fpassengers not to travel.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
