CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776449466
OL,3,CRail services set to resume after day
OL,4,Cof travel chaos
OL,6,FNetwork Rail confirmed that
OL,7,Fengineering teams have been assessing
OL,8,Fthe damage to the overhead line
OL,9,Fequipment, which carry 25,000 volts
OL,10,Fand are a "critical part of the
OL,11,Frailway".
OL,13,FServices are expected to resume from
OL,14,F7am on Friday, 17 April, with repair
OL,15,Fwork scheduled to take place overnight
OL,16,Fand will continue into the coming days.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
