PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776449466
OL,3,CRail services set to resume after day
OL,4,Cof travel chaos
OL,6,FThe timing of the disruption comes at
OL,7,Fa busy time as the city prepares to
OL,8,Fwelcome tens of thousands of visitors
OL,9,Fthis weekend for Britain First march,
OL,10,FManchester Marathon, and Manchester
OL,11,FCity vs Arsenal game.
OL,13,FChris Wright, North West route
OL,14,Fdirector for Network Rail, has
OL,15,Fapologised for the impact on
OL,16,Fpassengers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776449466
OL,3,CRail services set to resume after day
OL,4,Cof travel chaos
OL,6,F"The issue is complex but our teams
OL,7,Fare working hard to repair the railway
OL,8,Fas soon as possible," he said. "We
OL,9,Fhave worked closely with our train
OL,10,Foperator partners to keep passengers
OL,11,Fon the move wherever possible."
OL,13,FA wide range of operators were hit by
OL,14,Fthe issue, including Avanti West
OL,15,FCoast, CrossCountry, East Midlands
OL,16,FRailway, Northern, TransPennine
OL,17,FExpress, and Transport for Wales.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
