CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776449466
OL,3,CRail services set to resume after day
OL,4,Cof travel chaos
OL,6,FNetwork Rail and train operators
OL,7,Fcontinue to urge passengers to check
OL,8,Ffor the latest updates as repairs
OL,9,Fprogress.
OL,11,FSimon Turner, Head of Operational
OL,12,FReadiness at Avanti West Coast, said:
OL,13,F"Customers booked to travel on
OL,14,FThursday 16 April also have the option
OL,15,Fto make their journey on Friday 17
OL,16,FApril using their existing ticket.
OL,18,F"We strongly advise customers making
OL,19,Fjourneys on our Manchester route to
OL,20,Fcheck before they travel and would
OL,21,Flike to thank them for their patience.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
