CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776449466
OL,3,CRail services set to resume after day
OL,4,Cof travel chaos
OL,6,F"Anyone whose journey is delayed by 15
OL,7,Fminutes or more to claim Delay Repay
OL,8,Fcompensation."
OL,10,FNorthern has also warned rail
OL,11,Fpassengers to check before travelling.
OL,13,FA spokesperson at 6am on Friday said:
OL,14,F"As it stands, the line is still
OL,15,Fclosed. No trains are able to run to/
OL,16,Ffrom Manchester Piccadilly. We're
OL,17,Fhoping this to change later this
OL,18,Fmorning.
OL,26,@pD@NO]
