OL,3,CRail services set to resume after day
OL,4,Cof travel chaos
OL,6,F"Our advice remains to not travel on
OL,7,FPiccadilly trains until confirmed that
OL,8,Fthe station has reopened and trains
OL,9,Fhave started.
OL,11,F"If you were caught up in the
OL,12,Fdisruption yesterday, make sure you
OL,13,Feither claim a refund for not
OL,14,Ftravelling or compensation for delays
OL,15,Fof 15mins or more."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
